casebody.data:
Robert MOSER, Secretary of the Kansas Department of Health and Environment, et al., applicants,
v.
Kail MARIE, et al. No. 14A503. Supreme Court of the United States Nov. 10, 2014.

Opinion

UPON CONSIDERATION of the application of counsel for the applicants,

IT IS ORDERED that the preliminary injunction entered by the United States District Court for the District of Kansas on November 4, 2014, is hereby stayed pending receipt of a response, due on or before Tuesday, November 11, 2014, by 5 p.m. ET, and further order of the undersigned or of the Court.
